<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361386" n="1"/>
<opener>
<lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> <abbr>D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs>
</opener>
<p>
<lb/>Te rogo ut mihi parcas Vir Amicissime: quia
               <lb/>usque in hanc diem distuli responsion<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ad <abbr>hu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>maniss.<hi rend="sup">am</hi></abbr> tuam <rs key="B_1717-11-19_991170517038005501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1717-11-19">19 <abbr>No.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr></date> ad me datam:
               <lb/>negotia enim et assidua studia pro perficien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>da mea <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">exercitatione De Filtratione Liquo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum in Corporibus Animanti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, dilationis causa
               <lb/>fuerunt. Hodie ali<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs key="B_1717-12-08_991170517037805501" type="letter">tu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> mihi gratissimam acci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pio; pro qua et altera Tibi maximas refero
               <lb/>gratias: qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d optes me tanquam Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Collegam
               <lb/><del>huc </del>istuc aliquando ventur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>. Libentissime
               <lb/>hic moror: attamen si me honorific<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>movebunt non recusabo. <rs key="B_1717-11-12_991170517038205501" type="letter">Epistola<del>m</del></rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ad Te
               <lb/>misi <add><abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1717-11-12">12 <abbr>Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr></date></add> Vir <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr> minime erat inclusa ei,
               <lb/>quam dedi ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Marchion<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> Polen<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>. Curiosus
               <lb/>s<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sciendi caus<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> propter qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> hoc a me petis.
   <lb/>Inquir<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> anne tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Dieser Brief von Nic. I B. an Gadaldini ist anscheinend nicht erhalten.</note> pervenerint ad <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr>
<lb/>Secretari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1222289342" type="person">Gadaldin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, qua de re haud ambigo.
   <lb/>Statim deferam <rs key="B_1717-12-26_991170517059405501" type="letter">inclus<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> quam accepi, ad pos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam <rs key="place_GEO-3166740" type="place">Sinegale<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>. Hodie accepi <rs key="B_1717-12-01_991170515152805501" type="letter">litteras</rs> ab <abbr>Illus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>triss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> Tuo humaniss.<hi rend="sup">as</hi> mihique gratissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mas. Mitto ad Te tres florenos pro litterar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
               <lb/>expensis, rogoque ut quum scripseris ad
               <pb facs="1361388" n="2"/>
<lb/>ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>; <add>ei significes</add> meam promptitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>din<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> in persolvendis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipse<del> expe</del> insumpsit
               <lb/>in accipiendis meis litteris, suisque ad me
               <lb/>transmittendis. Commerci<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> enim meum
               <lb/>epistolare quamdiu vixero cum ipso Incom<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>parabili <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> Tuo continuare decerno.
                  <lb/>Monuit consanguine<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicola<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/>propediem ad patrios lares <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> redi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fore: quod si continget scribam roga<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>boque ut proximo mense Aprilis e<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ad me mittat. Interim te rogo ut c<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m
               <lb/>Lectiones Tuas absolveris huc te transferas.
               <lb/>Cupio enim ut salt<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> unico mense Domi
               <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> resideas sine ullis expensis: siquidem
               <lb/>Tua pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia mihi non sol<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> erit <abbr>gratiss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr>
<lb/>ver<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> etiam <abbr>utiliss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr> Opus enim habeo ut
               <lb/>nonnullas figuras mihi delinees; et ut
               <lb/>videas corrigasque qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad Mathesin specta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bunt in mea opella priusqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> e<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lo com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mitt<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>. Quando scribere voles ad <abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> mitte ad me epistolas. Nihil enim
               <lb/><del>ti </del>Tibi constabunt ibuntque cito ac tuto
               <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basil<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs>.
            </p>
<closer>Vale. <dateline>Dabam
   <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1717-12-09">9 X<hi rend="sup">bris</hi> 1717</date><supplied>.</supplied></dateline><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1717-12-11">11.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date></foreign></note>
</closer>
